## 5. Conference & Community Calendar

### Key Conferences

| Conference | Timing | Audience | Strategic Value |
|------------|--------|----------|-----------------|
| CASE Summit for Leaders | July | Senior VPs, CDOs | Executive relationships; brand visibility; thought leadership |
| CASE District Conferences | Feb–Mar | All advancement levels | Volume lead gen; mid-tier institution contacts; demos |
| Apra Prospect Development | August | Prospect researchers, data analysts | Champion-building; technical credibility; user feedback |
| AFP ICON | April | Broad nonprofit fundraisers | Market expansion beyond higher ed; brand awareness |
| Regional Apra Chapters | Year-round | Local researchers | Cost-effective; relationship-building; grassroots advocacy |

### Key Publications & Communities

- **CASE Currents:** Award-winning magazine; thought leadership opportunity
- **Chronicle of Philanthropy:** Broad nonprofit news; advertising reach
- **Inside Higher Ed:** Higher ed administration audience
- **LinkedIn Groups:** CASE, Apra, Higher Ed Advancement professionals

